Patch Set 4:

(1 comment)

Since currently, location_strategy is restricted to have one of the two choices - location_order and store_type, do we wait for the patch (https://review.openstack.org/#/c/336761) that lets adding any custom strategy module merge before editing this help text to reflect that?
Thanks.

Patch Set 4:

The patch Fei Long refers to [0] is a bit controversial.  I'd suggest letting this patch sit until after this Thursday's Glance meeting (it's on the agenda); at that point it will be clear whether you should just stick with what you have here, or re-write to fit Fei Long's patch and make his patch a dependency for this one.


[0] https://review.openstack.org/#/c/336761/

Patch Set 4:

It looks like the code change Fei Long mentions above isn't going to be accepted right away, so I think the best thing to do is to document these configuration options the way they are now (that is, restricted to the 2 values only).

For more info about the discussion around these options, please see the comments on https://review.openstack.org/#/c/336761/
